== Introduction ==

The preferences for the [[Image:Workbench_BIM.svg|24px]] [[BIM_Workbench|BIM Workbench]] can be found in the [[Preferences Editor|Preferences Editor]]. In the menu select {{MenuCommand|Edit → Preferences}} and then {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Workbench_BIM.svg|16px]] BIM}}. This group is only available if the BIM Workbench has been loaded in the current FreeCAD session.

There are three pages: [[#General_Settings|General Settings]], [[#Defaults|Defaults]] and [[#Native_IFC|Native IFC]].

Some advanced preferences can only be changed in the [[Std_DlgParameter|Parameter Editor]]. See [[Fine-tuning#BIM_Workbench|Fine-tuning]].

